Package com.github.tommyettinger.colorful.pure

Class Interpolations

java.lang.Object
com.github.tommyettinger.colorful.pure.Interpolations
@Deprecated public final class Interpolations extends Object
Deprecated.
Use Interpolations from digital instead.
Takes a linear value in the range of 0-1 and outputs a (usually) non-linear, interpolated value. The wiki docs on Interpolation are extremely useful for understanding how the different implementations here behave.
This class is mostly copied directly from libGDX. Changes have been made to avoid copying even more over.
